info.name: Ultimate Chipotle Aloo Patty Wrap.
info.description: Crispy & flavourful aloo patty is amped up with a generous drizzle of chipotle mayo and then gently wrapped with crunchy onions in a supple paratha. Add this to your wrap-list right away. I Calories (Kcals): 888 I Carbs (Gms): 86 I Proteins (Gms): 11 I Fats (Gms): 56

info.name: Classic Peppy Chicken Shawarma.
info.description: Wrap your taste buds around warm kuboos or rumali roti, with spiced chicken, creamy hummus, garlic mayo, pickled veggies, and french fries. You don't need a genie to satisfy this food craving!

info.name: Classic Smoky Chicken Shawarma.
info.description: Experience Arabic enchantment with thin, soft kuboos or rumali of your choice, enveloping marinated grilled chicken, hummus, pickles, french fries galore, and cabbage! Yalla Habibi!

info.name: Beetroot & Peanut Kebab
info.description: Savour the flavours of handpicked fresh beetroots and roasted peanuts with a subtle hint of spices. These royal beetroot kebabs are crisp on the outside and soft on the inside.

info.name: Gosht-E-Galouti Kebab (Mutton Galauti Kebab)
info.description: A melt-in-mouth culinary delicacy it can take the most enigmatic feasts a notch above. Tenderest mutton is minced to perfection & cooked with delicate spices to offer you a truly exquisite culinary experience.

info.name: Murgh Seekh Kebab
info.description: One of the most revered kebab delicacies, this culinary marvel is crafted with minced chicken that is elegantly spiced with royal spices and is served with a refreshing mint dip.

info.name: Aloo Chaap Tikki
info.description: A street favourite recipe that now resides in our royal kitchens. A mix of mashed potatoes, fresh coriander, chilies and onions, shallow-fried to form the perfect tea-time snack.

info.name: Murgh Malai Kebab (6 Pcs)
info.description: (6 Pcs) Brimming with impeccable flavours this rich kebab delicacy is as delectable as it is charming. Succulent chicken pieces are eloquently spiced with royal spices and then grilled to perfection to lend it the fascinating smoky flavour.

info.name: Murgh Haleem Kebab (6 pcs) & Murgh Kefta (6pcs) Combo
info.description: The coveted chicken haleem kebabs made with a melange of Hyderabadi spices is served alongside Murgh Kefta that is a fine amalgamation of finely minced fresh chicken and the choicest of spices.

info.name: Dahi Labneh Kebab (6 pcs) & Beetroot and Peanut Kebab (6 pcs) Combo
info.description: Subtly spiced with cumin and ginger, our Dahi Labneh Kebabs are served as a combo alongside kebabs made with handpicked fresh beetroots & crushed peanuts.

info.name: Beetroot & Peanut Kebab (6 pcs) & Hara Bhara Kebab (6 Pcs) Combo
info.description: Delicately spiced kebabs made with fresh beetroots & peanuts are served alongside the tender yet crispy Hara Bhara kebabs that are crafted with finely minced vegetables and shallow-fried to perfection.
